Salesforce Summer ’24 Release Notes
What’s New for the Salesforce Release Notes?

Monthly Release Notes
Release Update: Analytics
Unified Analytics Experiences
Embed CRM Analytics Dashboards in LWR Sites (Generally Available)
Get More Functionality with the New Dashboard Lightning Web Component

Embedded CRM Analytics dashboards can be added to your LWR sites, allowing customers to view and interact with visualizations of account data alongside their account information.

Where: This change applies to CRM Analytics in LWR sites accessed through Lightning Experience and Salesforce Classic.
How: Use the new CRM Analytics Dashboard Lightning web component in your Experience Cloud pages.
title: Embedding CRM Analytics Dashboards
